{"tid":2278471,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"想搬走唔同屋企人住之前 有啲咩係一定要帶走？","createTime":"2020-11-09T07:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T08:55:19.000Z","uid":258112,"like":9,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"227e6fc825a0700aaaf5ace4a68ed46047143b1a","tid":2278471,"uid":258112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:35:58.000Z","msg":"今年year2<br />\n本身同緊老豆老母一齊住<br />\n宜家計劃緊同男朋友搬出嚟住<br />\n有搵兼職做 租 水電煤都應付到 <br />\n所以錢唔成問題<br />\n<br />\n但係老豆老母未知我會同男朋友一齊住<br />\n就算知道咗都會好麻煩<br />\n所以想拎曬啲野就直接搬<br />\n斷關係斷得乾乾淨淨<br />\n唔洗返去問佢地拎野嘅時候又煩住曬或者拎唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 由細到大老豆老母乜都管住曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住係屋企就無得出夜街 出個去都要講聲問聲<br />\n自己一個人係房想做下自己野都要嘈住曬<br />\n連本passport都仲係佢地到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知以為我仲係幼稚園啲細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74321b63592600e62c2391e2cd9177d36ccb3862","tid":2278471,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"100蚊樓上嘅嘢"},{"pid":"990df6b5c306d066fb12d7631d6f2b33a0787bc3","tid":2278471,"uid":50744,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"咩理由搬出去都好<br />\n記住他日無論任何原因都唔好搬返屋企住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝福你"},{"pid":"e57318602910eaa305a929d59a75e2d1fbb036a1","tid":2278471,"uid":244215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"要搵到一間兼職都可以當入息證明嘅單位"},{"pid":"c06113b9a0dbbaed65561416ebe1537b87b1d366","tid":2278471,"uid":229212,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"記得上網改地址<br />\n以防d信寄返去舊屋<br />\n到時又要返轉頭拎信"},{"pid":"1e299daa4a562c0641519ed97b01a7e1e5df08d6","tid":2278471,"uid":195607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":